20considering%20the%20nature%20of%20event%2C%20the%20board%20allowed%20each%20player%20to%20have%20family%20members'%20company%20for%20one%20game.%20It%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20revealed%20for%20which%20game%20the%20players%20have%20decided%20to%20get%20the%20board's%20approval.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20issuing%20the%20new%20policy%20for%20family%20members%2C%20the%20BCCI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20it%20intends%20to%20%26quot%3Bensure%20professional%20standards%20and%20operational%20efficiency%20during%20tours%20and%20series%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20policy%2C%20which%20is%20in%20possession%20of%20PTI%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20exceptions%20or%20deviations%20must%20be%20pre-approved%20by%20the%20Chairman%20of%20the%20Selection%20Committee%20and%20Head%20Coach.%20Non-compliance%20may%20lead%20to%20disciplinary%20action%20as%20deemed%20appropriate%20by%20the%20BCCI%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Board%20has%20warned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdditionally%2C%20the%20BCCI%20reserves%20the%20right%20to%20take%20disciplinary%20action%20against%20a%20player%20which%20may%20include%20sanction%20against%20the%20concerned%20player%20from%20participating%20in%20all%20BCCI%20conducted%20tournaments%20including%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20deduction%20from%20retainer%20amount%2Fmatch%20fees%20under%20BCCI%20Player%20contract%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20scheduled%20to%20take%20on%20Bangladesh%20in%20their%20opening%20match%20on%20February%2020.%20Subsequently%2C%20the%20team%20will%20square%20off%20against%20Pakistan%20on%20February%2023%20and%20New%20Zealand%20on%20March%2002.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739857080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fqfp0cl18_anushka-sharma-bcci_625x300_18_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Findia-stars-permitted-to-stay-with-wives-during-champions-trophy-but-on-this-bcci-condition-77359