0Question%20With%20No%20Kyiv%20On%20The%20Table%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20a%20tentative%20start%20to%20ending%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%2C%20about%20to%20near%20a%20three-year%20mark%2C%20both%20sides%20said%20the%20first%20high-level%20meet%20since%20the%202022%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%20is%20unlikely%20to%20result%20in%20concrete%20outcomes.%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20and%20US%20National%20Security%20Advisor%20Mike%20Waltz%20and%20Russian%20officials%2C%20including%20Foreign%20Minister%20Sergey%20Lavrov%2C%20will%20also%20discuss%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20The%20talks%20come%20after%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20held%20talks%20with%20his%20Russian%20counterpart%20Vladimir%20Putin%2C%20while%20the%20American%20defence%20chief%20rule%20out%20Ukraine%20joining%20NATO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKremlin%20spokesman%20Dmitry%20Peskov%20told%20reporters%20the%20talks%20would%20be%20%26quot%3Bprimarily%20devoted%20to%20restoring%20the%20whole%20complex%20of%20Russian-American%20relations%26quot%3B%2C%20alongside%20discussions%20on%20%26quot%3Bpossible%20negotiations%20on%20a%20Ukrainian%20resolution%2C%20and%20organising%20a%20meeting%20between%20the%20two%20presidents%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKyiv%20was%20not%20invited%20to%20the%20talks%2C%20prompting%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20to%20accuse%20the%20US%20of%20wanting%20%26quot%3Bto%20please%26quot%3B%20Putin%20by%20%26quot%3Bnow%20saying%20things%20that%20are%20very%20favourable%26quot%3B%20to%20him.%20Zelensky%20said%20%26quot%3Bwe%20will%20not%20sign%20just%20anything%20in%20order%20to%20be%20applauded%26quot%3B%20and%20stressed%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20fate%20of%20our%20state%20for%20generations%20to%20come%26quot%3B%20was%20at%20stake.%20Even%20so%2C%20he%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20will%20definitely%20not%20be%20a%20Ukrainian%20victory%20without%20US%20support%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20said%20last%20week%20he%20was%20prepared%20to%20meet%20Putin%2C%20but%20only%20after%20Kyiv%20and%20its%20allies%20had%20a%20common%20position%20on%20ending%20the%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20push%20for%20a%20swift%20resolution%20to%20the%20three-year%20conflict%20in%20Ukraine%20is%20Moscow's%20opportunity%20to%20press%20its%20long-standing%20demands%20regarding%20Washington's%20military%20presence%20in%20Europe.%20Moscow%20has%20sought%20to%20roll%20back%20NATO's%20presence%20in%20Europe%2C%20with%20Putin%20demanding%20before%20the%20February%202022%20invasion%20for%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20military%20alliance's%20troops%20equipment%20and%20bases%20out%20of%20several%20eastern%20members%20that%20were%20under%20Moscow's%20sphere%20of%20influence%20during%20the%20Cold%20War.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoscow%20is%20buoyed%20by%20advances%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20pushing%20back%20Ukrainian%20troops%20across%20the%201%2C000-kilometre-long%20front%20line%20and%20regaining%20control%20of%20a%20village%20in%20the%20western%20Kursk%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EContentious%20Gaza%20%26quot%3BRelocation%26quot%3B%20Plan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERubio%20will%20also%20hold%20talks%20with%20Saudi%20officials%20on%20a%20controversial%20US%20proposal%20for%20Gaza%2C%20days%20after%20Trump's%20proposal%20to%20%26quot%3Btake%20over%26quot%3B%20Gaza%20and%20relocate%20millions%20of%20Palestinians%20from%20the%20besieged%20enclave.%20While%20the%20US%20has%20indicated%20it%20is%20open%20to%20alternative%20proposals%20from%20Arab%20governments%2C%20Rubio%20has%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20only%20plan%20is%20the%20Trump%20plan.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20State%20Department%20confirmed%20that%20Rubio%20met%20with%20Saudi%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed%20bin%20Salman%20Al%20Saud%2C%20during%20which%20he%20underlined%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20Gaza%20arrangement%20that%20contributes%20to%20regional%20security%2C%20Xinhua%20news%20agency%20reported.%20The%20official%20Saudi%20Press%20Agency%20(SPA)%20reported%20that%20they%20discussed%20regional%20and%20global%20developments%20and%20efforts%20to%20achieve%20security%20and%20stability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20days%20ahead%20of%20a%20regional%20Gulf%20Cooperation%20Council%20summit%20in%20Riyadh%20to%20formalise%20proposals%2C%20as%20Egypt%20plans%20a%20%26quot%3Bcomprehensive%20vision%26quot%3B%20for%20Gaza%20reconstruction%20that%20does%20not%20involve%20population%20displacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEurope%20Left%20In%20The%20Cold%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZelensky%20warned%20that%20Europe%20was%20in%20a%20weak%20position%20if%20it%20could%20not%20rely%20on%20the%20US%20security%20umbrella.%20While%20%26quot%3Breadiness%20has%20increased%26quot%3B%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20%26quot%3Bin%20terms%20of%20troop%20strength%2C%20the%20number%20of%20combat%20troops%2C%20the%20fleet%2C%20the%20air%20force%2C%20the%20drones...%20I%20honestly%20think%20that%20Europe%20is%20weak%20today%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20European%20leaders%20gathered%20in%20Paris%20for%20an%20emergency%20security%20summit%2C%20Russia's%20Lavrov%20said%20he%20saw%20no%20point%20in%20them%20taking%20part%20in%20any%20Ukraine%20talks.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what%20they%20would%20do%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table...%20if%20they%20are%20going%20to%20sit%20at%20the%20negotiating%20table%20with%20the%20aim%20of%20continuing%20war%2C%20then%20why%20invite%20them%20there%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Moscow.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReturn%20Of%20A%20Diplomatic%20Pariah%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20with%20Europe%20unable%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20common%20base%20for%20US-Russia%20talks%2C%20diplomatic%20pariah%20under%20the%20Joe%20Biden-led%20administration%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20been%20brought%20back%20into%20the%20fold%20with%20Trump's%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia's%20entry%20into%20the%20spotlight%20comes%20after%20the%20oil-rich%20power%20watched%20Qatar%20mediate%20a%20hard-won%20yet%20fragile%20truce%20in%20the%20Israel-Hamas%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20has%20walked%20a%20long%20road%20to%20international%20legitimacy%20after%20the%20disappearance%20and%20death%20of%20dissident%20Saudi%20journalist%20Jamal%20Khashoggi%20in%20Turkey%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20historic%20ally%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20has%20avoided%20choosing%20sides%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20it%20also%20maintains%20close%20relations%20with%20Russia%20on%20energy%20policy%20while%20promising%20hundreds%20of%20millions%20of%20dollars%20in%20humanitarian%20aid%20to%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739856180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fuhis7bj8_us-russia-talks-marco-rubio-crown-prince_625x300_18_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-russia-talks-leave-out-ukraine-saudi-back-as-dealbreaker-to-end-war-7735546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US-Russia%20ties%20and%20Ukraine%20war%20will%20be%20on%20the%20table%20as%20top%20diplomats%20from%20Moscow%20and%20Washington%20meet%20in%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20Riyadh%2C%20while%20a%20concerned%20Europe%20remains%20in%20the%20shadows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-russia-talks-leave-out-ukraine-saudi-back-as-dealbreaker-to-end-war-7735546%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Musk's%20xAI%20unveils%20new%20AI%20chatbot%20Grok-3%20to%20rival%20ChatGPT%2C%20DeepSeek%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739856082000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fmusk-s-xai-unveils-new-ai-chatbot-grok-3-to-rival-chatgpt-deepseek-125021800249_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Grok-3%20is%20ro