2%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshamshabad-orr-donuts-2-students-in-fortuner-bmw-perform-stunts-on-busy-hyderabad-road-arrested-7735442%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mystery%20vs%20History%3A%20Selection%20curve%20ball%20pits%20Kuldeep%20vs%20Varun%20for%20spinner's%20spot%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739851427000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118345269%2Cimgsize-82600.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fmystery-vs-history-selection-curve-ball-pits-kuldeep-yadav-against-varun-chakravarthy-for-spinners-spot-in-indias-playing-xi%2Farticleshow%2F118345147.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20selectors%2C%20led%20by%20Ajit%20Agarkar%2C%20surprised%20many%20by%20replacing%20opener%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20with%20mystery%20spinner%20Varun%20Chakravarthy%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy.%20Despite%20four%20spinners%20already%20in%20the%20squad%2C%20Varun's%20inclusion%20raised%20eyebrows.%20The%20key%20decision%20now%20revolves%20around%20who%20will%20play%20in%20the%20XI%20between%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20and%20Varun%20Chakravarthy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22GAURAV%20GUPTA%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fmystery-vs-history-selection-curve-ball-pits-kuldeep-yadav-against-varun-chakravarthy-for-spinners-spot-in-indias-playing-xi%2Farticleshow%2F118345147.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%2250%20Film%20Stars%2C%20Industrialists%2C%20Diplomats%20Invited%20To%20BJP's%20Delhi%20Oath%20Event%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Delhi%20will%20take%20oath%20at%20the%20iconic%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20on%20Thursday%20in%20a%20grand%20ceremony%20that%20will%20be%20attended%20by%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20ministers%20and%20all%20the%20allies.%20Sources%20said%20plans%20are%20in%20progress%20to%20make%20the%20party's%20return%20to%20power%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20after%2026%20years%20a%20truly%20memorable%20event.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceremony%20will%20begin%20at%204.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20colourful%20musical%20programme%20will%20be%20held%20on%20the%20stage%20of%20Ramlila%20Maidan%20before%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony%2C%20in%20which%20Kailash%20Kher%20will%20also%20perform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Ministers%20and%20Deputy%20Chief%20Ministers%20of%2020%20states%20will%20attend%20the%20mega%20event.%20Diplomats%20of%20major%20countries%20have%20also%20been%20invited.%20BJP%20leaders%20and%20workers%20from%20other%20states%20who%20campaigned%20in%20the%20Delhi%20elections%20are%20also%20expected%20to%20be%20present%20on%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20than%2050%20film%20stars%20and%20industrialists%2C%20will%20be%20present.%20Besides%2C%20Farmers%20of%20Delhi%2C%20beneficiaries%20of%20central%20government%20schemes%20including%20laadli%20sisters%2C%20and%20common%20people%20from%20Delhi%20will%20also%20be%20invited%20to%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20spiritual%20leaders%20of%20the%20country%20will%20be%20represented%20by%20Baba%20Ramdev%2C%20Swami%20Chidananda%2C%20Baba%20Bageshwar%20Dhirendra%20Shastri%20and%20other%20religious%20figures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%2C%20however%2C%20is%20no%20word%20on%20who%20is%20going%20to%20get%20the%20top%20job.%20Initially%20it%20was%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20France%20and%20the%20US%20that%20had%20delayed%20a%20decision.%20But%20now%2C%20even%20two%20days%20after%20his%20return%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20announcement%2C%20ratcheting%20up%20the%20suspense.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Parvesh%20Verma%20--%20the%20son%20of%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Saheb%20Singh%20Verma%20--%20is%20seen%20as%20the%20front-runner%20in%20the%20race%2C%20sources%20said%20the%20list%20of%20probables%20has%20no%20less%20than%2015%20names%20that%20also%20include%20candidates%20for%20cabinet%20and%20the%20Assembly%20Speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENine%20names%20will%20be%20chosen%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20and%20Delhi%20will%20have%20eight%20ministers%20including%20the%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2048%20BJP%20MLAs%20are%20expected%20to%20meet%20on%20Wednesday%20to%20select%20their%20leader%2C%20who%20will%20succeed%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party's%20Atishi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20election%20held%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20scripted%20a%20massive%20comeback%2C%20winning%2048%20of%20the%20assembly's%2070%20seats%20and%20confining%20AAP%20to%2022%20--%20down%20from%2062.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20end%20to%20the%2010-year%20rule%20of%20AAP%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20massive%20corruption%20allegations%20against%20its%20leaders%2C%20including%20then%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal.%20A%20number%20of%20its%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20and%20his%20then%20deputy%20Manish%20Sisodia%20--%20spent%20months%20in%20jail.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20the%20alleged%20liquor%20policy%20scam%2C%20the%20%26quot%3BSheesh%20Mahal%26quot%3B%20allegations%20against%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20-%20the%20Rs%2033.6%20crore%20revamp%20that%20that%20turned%20the%20official%20residence%20of%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20into%20an%20opulent%20bungalow%20suitable%20for%20the%20uber-rich%20-%20appeared%20to%20have%20taken%20the%20sheen%20off%20AAP%20that%20thrived%20on%20its%20governance%20records%20for%20the%20better%20part%20of%20the%20last%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739851380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fuoubr1r8_bjp-flag-generic-_625x300_08_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhi-chief-minister-not-named-sources-say-date-venue-for-oath-fixed-7732784%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20new%2