%20by%20its%20Endeavor%20Air%20subsidiary%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20single-aircraft%20accident%20with%2076%20passengers%20and%20four%20crew%20members%20on%20board.%20The%2016-year-old%20CRJ900%2C%20made%20by%20Canada's%20Bombardier%20and%20powered%20by%20GE%20Aerospace%20engines%2C%20can%20seat%20up%20to%2090%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%2018%20of%20the%20people%20injured%20were%20passengers%20and%20were%20taken%20to%20area%20hospitals%2C%20Delta%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20those%20injured%2C%20two%20were%20airlifted%20to%20trauma%20centres%2C%20and%20a%20child%20was%20transported%20to%20a%20children's%20hospital%2C%20said%20Supervisor%20Lawrence%20Saindon%20of%20Peel%20Regional%20Paramedic%20Services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Toronto%20airport%20was%20shut%20down%20for%20more%20than%20two%20hours%20before%20departures%20and%20arrivals%20resumed.%20This%20led%20to%20ground%20delays%20and%20diversions%20to%20other%20airports%20including%20Montreal-Trudeau%20International%20Airport%2C%20which%20said%20it%20was%20preparing%20to%20receive%20several%20diverted%20flights%20that%20might%20cause%20further%20delays.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFlint%20said%20on%20Monday%20evening%20there%20would%20be%20some%20operational%20impact%20and%20delays%20at%20Toronto%20Airport%20over%20the%20next%20few%20days%20while%20two%20runways%20remained%20closed%20for%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20of%20Canada%20(TSB)%20said%20it%20was%20deploying%20a%20team%20of%20investigators%2C%20and%20the%20U.S.%20National%20Transportation%20Safety%20Board%20said%20a%20team%20of%20investigators%20would%20assist%20Canada's%20TSB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan's%20Mitsubishi%20Heavy%20Industries%2C%20which%20closed%20a%20deal%20to%20buy%20the%20CRJ%20aircraft%20program%20from%20Bombardier%20in%202020%2C%20said%20it%20was%20aware%20of%20the%20incident%20and%20would%20fully%20cooperate%20with%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20crash%20in%20Canada%20followed%20other%20recent%20crashes%20in%20North%20America.%20An%20Army%20helicopter%20collided%20with%20a%20CRJ-700%20passenger%20jet%20in%20Washington%2C%20killing%2067%20people%2C%20while%20at%20least%20seven%20people%20died%20when%20a%20medical%20transport%20plane%20crashed%20in%20Philadelphia%20and%2010%20were%20killed%20in%20a%20passenger%20plane%20crash%20in%20Alaska.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739849640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fbm0aieag_canada-plane-crash_625x300_18_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-passenger-captures-his-dramatic-rescue-from-inside-delta-plane-that-flipped-upside-down-on-landing-in-canada-7734989%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%2018%20people%20were%20injured%20after%20a%20Delta%20Air%20Lines%20regional%20jet%20flipped%20upside%20down%20upon%20landing%20at%20Canada's%20Toronto%20Pearson%20Airport%20on%20Monday%20amid%20windy%20weather%20following%20a%20snowstorm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fvideo-passenger-captures-his-dramatic-rescue-from-inside-delta-plane-that-flipped-upside-down-on-landing-in-canada-7734989%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Julianne%20Moore%20reacts%20to%20Trump%20banning%20her%20book%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739849541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118344736%2Cimgsize-60468.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fjulianne-moore-expresses-heartbreak-over-ban-of-her-book-by-trump%2Farticleshow%2F118344710.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F118344710.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJulianne%20Moore%20