EAndrew%20Harnik%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20cut%20an%20ad%20urging%20Trump%20to%20fire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%20watchdog%20group%20Common%20Cause%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECommon%20Cause%20said%20it%20had%20a%20%24115%2C000%20deal%20to%20run%20ads%20in%20the%20Post's%20Tuesday%20print%20editions.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Post%20initially%20approved%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20ad%2C%20and%20didn't%20say%20why%20it%20was%20rejected%2C%20the%20org%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%20scrapped%20an%20ad%20calling%20for%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20%26quot%3Bfire%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20that%20was%20slated%20to%20run%20in%20some%20of%20its%20Tuesday%20print%20editions%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20organizations%20that%20ordered%20the%20ad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdvocacy%20group%20Common%20Cause%20had%20agreed%20to%20pay%20%24115%2C000%20to%20the%20Post%20to%20run%20an%20ad%20criticizing%20billionaire%20Elon%20Musk%20wrapped%20around%20the%20newspapers%20and%20a%20similar%20ad%20inside%20the%20paper%2C%20the%20organization%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ads%20are%20part%20of%20a%20bigger%20campaign%20by%20Common%20Cause%20called%20%26quot%3BFire%20Elon%20Musk%2C%26quot%3B%20urging%20people%20to%20sign%20a%20petition%20calling%20for%20Musk's%20removal%20as%20the%20head%20of%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-department-of-government-efficiency%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ad%2C%20which%20Common%20Cause%20later%20posted%20on%20its%20website%2C%20features%20Elon%20Musk%20laughing%20behind%20an%20image%20of%20the%20White%20House%2C%20and%20says%20in%20large%20text%2C%20%26quot%3BWho's%20running%20this%20country%