ca%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20entire%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%2C%20which%20touches%20the%20US%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20Cuba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DyVJkGqLM5WQ%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20Mexican%20President%20Claudia%20Sheinbaum%20said%20that%20Mexico%20will%20sue%20Google%20if%20the%20tech%20giant%20does%20not%20change%20the%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20label%20to%20cover%20only%20the%20portion%20of%20the%20body%20of%20water%20under%20US%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20that%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20January%2020%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-day-one-agenda-executive-orders-inauguration-day-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20rename%20the%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20Mexico%26quot%3B%20to%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America%26quot%3B%20pertains%20only%20to%20its%20own%20continental%20shelf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20talking%20about%2022%20nautical%20miles%2C%20not%20the%20entire%20gulf%2C%26quot%3B%20Sheinbaum%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20Google%20is%20also%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20continental%20shelves%20of%20Mexico%20and%20Cuba.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mexican%20government%20has%20been%20discussing%20this%20matter%20with%20Google%20since%20January.%20Sheinbaum%20shared%20her%20government's%20response%20to%20Google's%20most%20recent%20letter%20on%20its%20maps%2C%20saying%20that%20under%20no%20circumstances%20will%20Mexico%20accept%20the%20renaming%20of%20any%20geographical%20area%20that%20includes%20its%20national%20territory%20or%20that%20falls%20under%20its%20jurisdiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAny%20reference%20to%20the%20'Gulf%20of%20America'%20initiative%20on%20your%20Google%20Maps%20platform%20must%20be%20exclusively%20limited%20to%20the%20marine%20area%20under%20US%20jurisdiction%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20read.%20%26quot%3BAny%20extension%20beyond%20that%20zone%20exceeds%20the%20authority%20of%20any%20national%20government%20or%20private%20entity.%20Should%20that%20be%20the%20case%2C%20the%20Government%20of%20Mexico%20will%20take%20the%20appropriate%20legal%20actions%20as%20deemed%20necessary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESheinbaum%2C%20who%20noted%20last%20week%20that%20a%20civil%20suit%20was%20possible%2C%20said%20Monday%20that%20the%20Mexican%20government%20would%20await%20Google's%20response%20before%20proceeding%20with%20legal%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reached%20out%20to%20Google%20but%20has%20not%20yet%20received%20a%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Donald%20Trump%20renames%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20as%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20One.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67af68986630eb10385cac11%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20speaking%20to%20the%20press%20beside%20a%20large%20map%20that%20says%20%26quot%3BGulf%20of%20America.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EROBERTO%20SCHMIDT%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20January%207%2C%20in%20the%20lead-up%20to%20the%20inauguration%20of%20his%20second%20term%2C%20Trump%20stated%20his%20intention%20to%20rename%20the%20Gulf.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20be%20changing%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Gulf%20of%20Mexico%20to%20the%20Gulf%20of%20America%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20a%20beautiful%20name%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it's%20appropriate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20Sheinbaum%20sarcastically%20remarked%20that%20North%20America%20should%20be%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparts-us-america-mexicana-mexican-president-says-donald-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAm%C3%A9rica%20Mexicana%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E