e%20IPL%202025%20opening%20match%20at%20their%20home%20ground%20Eden%20Gardens%20on%20March%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20acknowledging%20that%20RCB%20finished%20strong%20in%20IPL%202024%20under%20a%20similar%20scenario%2C%20Chopra%20pointed%20out%20that%20their%20final%20league%20game%20against%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20could%20be%20a%20tough%20challenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20Chopra%20dissected%20the%20schedule%20for%20multiple%20franchises%2C%20offering%20insights%20into%20potential%20advantages%20and%20obstacles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20RCB%2C%20he%20noted%20that%20their%20campaign%20opens%20against%20KKR%20in%20Kolkata%20on%20March%2022%20and%20ends%20with%20a%20reverse%20fixture%20against%20the%20same%20opponents%20in%20Bengaluru%20on%20May%2017.%20Given%20that%20KKR%20dominated%20RCB%20in%20both%20encounters%20last%20season%2C%20Chopra%20suggested%20that%20facing%20them%20again%20at%20such%20crucial%20junctures%20could%20be%20a%20double-edged%20sword.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20interesting%20for%20Bengaluru.%20They%20have%20three%20of%20their%20last%20four%20and%20four%20of%20their%20last%20six%20games%20at%20home.%20They%20have%20more%20matches%20at%20home%20towards%20the%20back%20end.%20It%20used%20to%20be%20a%20problem%20earlier%20but%20the%20last%20season%20made%20you%20understand%20that%20they%20are%20quite%20okay%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20remained%20cautious%20about%20the%20KKR%20factor%2C%20reminding%20fans%20that%20the%20Kolkata-based%20franchise%20has%20had%20the%20upper%20hand%20in%20recent%20meetings.%20While%20RCB%20lost%20convincingly%20at%20home%20to%20KKR%20last%20year%2C%20they%20also%20fell%20short%20by%20just%20one%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20won%20the%20last%20few%20matches%20at%20home%20and%20they%20happened%20to%20qualify.%20So%20if%20we%20see%20the%20last%20year's%20template%2C%20it%20just%20looks%20alright.%2