%20with%20garlic%2C%20extra-virgin%20olive%20oil%2C%20lemon%20juice%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20rosemary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20like%20to%20put%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20paprika%20on%20them%20for%20the%20smokiness%20and%20color%2C%26quot%3B%20Falsini%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%2C%20place%20the%20fish%20and%20potatoes%20in%20a%20pan%20and%20add%20lemon%20slices%2C%20crushed%20garlic%2C%20and%20parsley.%20Season%20the%20fish%20with%20salt%20and%20extra-virgin%20olive%20oil%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFalsini%20recommends%20cooking%20the%20fish%20at%20350%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20The%20dish%20should%20be%20ready%20in%2045%20to%2050%20minutes%20if%20you're%20cooking%20about%20three%20pounds%20of%20fish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20check%20if%20your%20whole%20fish%20is%20ready%2C%20Falsini%20recommends%20pulling%20on%20the%20spine%20on%20the%20back%20of%20the%20fish.%20If%20the%20spine%20comes%20off%2C%20the%20fish%20is%20ready.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20just%20remove%20the%20flesh%20with%20a%20spoon%20and%20finish%20with%20some%20more%20olive%20oil%2C%20salt%2C%20and%20fresh%20lemon%20juice.%20Dinner%20is%20served!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-best-fish-at-home-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739833722000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67b3b9506630eb10385cd39d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-best-fish-at-home-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michelin-starred%20chef%20Massimo%20Falsini%20specializes%20in%20seafood%20dishes%20at%20Caruso's%2C%20the%20restaurant%20at%20Rosewood%20Miramar%20Beach%20resort%20in%20Santa%20Barbara.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22akonstantinides%40businessinsider.com%20(Anneta%20Konstantinides)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-cook-best-fish-at-home-2025-2%22