%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnadav-shoval-ouster-tech-startup-openweb-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eousted%20as%20CEO%20of%20OpenWeb%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20its%20board%20in%20a%20messy%20public%20battle%2C%20is%20back%20with%20the%20adtech%20company%20in%20an%20advisor%20role%2C%20Business%20Insider%20has%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20email%20to%20employees%20sent%20on%20Friday%20morning%20and%20obtained%20by%20BI%2C%20OpenWeb's%20interim%20CEO%2C%20Tim%20Harvey%2C%20announced%20that%20the%20company%20and%20Shoval%20had%20%26quot%3Breached%20a%20mutually%20agreed%20resolution%26quot%3B%20in%20which%20Shoval%20would%20remain%20connected%20to%20the%20company%20as%20a%20senior%20advisor%20to%20its%20chief%20executive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Friday%2C%20the%20company%20published%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.openweb.com%2Fblog%2Fnadav-shoval-as-senior-advisor-to-ceo-tim-harvey%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epost%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20its%20website%20confirming%20the%20move.%20OpenWeb%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20resolved%20our%20differences%2C%26quot%3B%20Shoval%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BThe%20company%20remains%20committed%20to%20its%20mission%20of%20OpenWeb%2C%20and%20I'm%20excited%20to%20continue%20to%20support%20the%20mission%20in%20my%20role%20as%20senior%20advisor%20to%20the%20CEO.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20settlement%20caps%20months%20of%20drama%20at%20OpenWeb%2C%20which%20began%20in%20mid-2024%20after%20Shoval%20and%20some%20board%20members%20disagreed%20over%20a%20potential%20investment%20in%20the%20company%20from%20BlackRock%2C%20Shoval%20previously%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnadav-shoval-ouster-tech-startup-openweb-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einterview%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20relationship%20between%20Shoval%20and%20the%20bo