0that%20scrapped%20Article%20370%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20in%202019.%20He%20is%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20Mr%20Shah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20objected%20to%20the%20selection%20as%20the%20law%20on%20appointment%20of%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20challenged%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20will%20hear%20the%20matter%20on%20Saturday.%20The%20party%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20government%20wants%20control%20of%20Election%20Commission%20and%20is%20not%20concerned%20about%20its%20credibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%2C%20sources%20said%2C%20did%20not%20want%20to%20postpone%20the%20selection%20process%20as%20it%20would%20leave%20a%20vacancy%20in%20the%20poll%20commission.%20The%20court%20had%20not%20stayed%20the%20appointment%20and%20legal%20opinion%20was%20sought%20before%20making%20the%20move%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20parliament%20formed%20a%20law%20on%20the%20matter%20in%202023%2C%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20was%20appointed%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister.%20Traditionally%2C%20the%20seniormost%20of%20the%20two%20remaining%20Election%20commissioners%20gets%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Chief%20Election%20Commissioner%20And%20Other%20Election%20Commissioners%20(Appointment%2C%20Conditions%20of%20Service%20And%20Term%20of%20Office)%20Act%2C%202023%2C%20a%20committee%20headed%20by%20the%20law%20minister%20has%20to%20shortlist%20five%20candidates%20and%20the%20selection%20team%20-%20the%20Prime%20Minister%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20and%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20--%20has%20to%20make%20the%20final%20selection.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20parliamentary%20law%20had%20set%20aside%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20guideline%20that%20made%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20a%20part%20of%20the%20selection%20committee.%20The%20replacement%20of%20the%20CJI%20with%20a%20cabinet%20minister%20has%20been%20challenged%20in%20court%2C%20with%20petitioners%20alleging%20that%20it%20interfered%20with%20the%20balance%20of%20power%20in%20the%20committee%20and%20affected%20its%20neutrality.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739818380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F56jsmht_gyanesh-kumar_625x300_17_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanesh-kumar-appointed-new-chief-election-commissioner-7733534%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Election%20Commissioner%20Gyanesh%20Kumar%2C%20the%20senior%20of%20the%20two%20election%20commissioners%20after%20Chief%20Election%20Commission%20Rajiv%20Kumar%2C%20will%20succeed%20him%2C%20the%20government%20announced%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fgyanesh-kumar-appointed-new-chief-election-commissioner-7733534%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump%20dispatches%20NY%20real%20estate%20dealmaker%20to%20solve%20global%20crises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739818261000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F9729%2Flive%2F1249f150-ecbb-11ef-9f8d-f789b67e94e6.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgq0q0eq28no%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Steve%20Witkoff%20will%20play%20a%20key%20role%20in%20America's%20talks%20with%20Russia%20to%20end%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A307%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgq0q0eq28no%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgq0q0eq28no.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcgq0q0eq28no.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Mission%3A%20Impossible%20%E2%80%93%20The%20Final%20Reckoning%E2%80%99%20Weighs%20Cannes%20F