tion%20of%20strategic%20importance%2C%20aggressively%20pursuing%20bilateral%20trade%20agreements%20and%20reducing%20reliance%20on%20any%20single%20market.%20With%20India's%20GDP%20surpassing%20%244%20trillion%20in%202024%20-%20securing%20its%20place%20as%20the%20world's%20fifth-largest%20economy%20-%20the%20government%20is%20now%20aiming%20to%20double%20foreign%20trade%20to%20%242%20trillion%20by%202030.%20This%20momentum%20is%20further%20bolstered%20by%20record%20foreign%20direct%20investment%2C%20which%20reached%20%2485%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20success%20of%20initiatives%20like%20'Make%20in%20India'%20and%20the%20country's%20expanding%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecent%20developments%20reinforce%20this%20trajectory.%20During%20his%20recent%20visit%20to%20the%20US%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20engaged%20in%20high-level%20talks%20that%20led%20to%20concrete%20measures%20for%20resolving%20trade%20and%20tariff%20disputes.%20India's%20commitment%20to%20increasing%20US%20oil%20and%20gas%20imports%20by%20%2410%20billion%20strengthens%20a%20growing%20energy%20partnership%2C%20with%20bilateral%20trade%20expected%20to%20reach%20%24500%20billion%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrengthening%20Defence%20and%20Technological%20Dominance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20economic%20policy%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20reshaping%20India's%20defence%20and%20security%20strategy.%20With%20defence%20spending%20surging%20to%20%2481.4%20billion%20in%202024%2C%20India%20is%20aggressively%20modernising%20its%20forces%20and%20deepening%20strategic%20alliances.%20Key%20defence%20agreements%20with%20the%20US%20include%20advanced%20negotiations%20for%20procuring%20F-35%20fighter%20jets%20and%20a%20ten-year%20defence%20cooperation%20pact%20-%20moves%20that%20solidify%20India's%20military%20capabilities%20and%20reinforce%20its%20push%20for%20self-reliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20the%20transformative%20power%20of%20technology%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20also%20positioned%20India%20as%20a%20global%20tech%20powerhouse.%20Strategic%20investments%20in%20AI%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20digital%20infrastructure%20aim%20to%20expand%20India's%20digital%20economy%20to%20%241%20trillion%20by%202030.%20A%20major%20semiconductor%20deal%20with%20the%20US%20marks%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20reducing%20India's%20reliance%20on%20China%2C%20strengthening%20its%20technological%20self-sufficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ETurning%20Tariffs%20Into%20An%20Opportunity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20US%20tariffs%20on%20Indian%20products%20might%20seem%20like%20a%20setback%2C%20they%20could%20drive%20long-term%20benefits%20by%20accelerating%20domestic%20innovation%20and%20strengthening%20India's%20industrial%20base.%20Importantly%2C%20President%20Trump%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20these%20tariffs%20are%20part%20of%20a%20broader%20global%20strategy%20and%20not%20a%20punitive%20measure%20against%20India.%20With%20reduced%20access%20to%20the%20US%20market%2C%20Indian%20industries%20are%20being%20pushed%20to%20upgrade%20technology%2C%20improve%20product%20quality%2C%20and%20streamline%20production%20to%20remain%20competitive%20globally.%20This%20challenge%20could%20catalyse%20structural%20reforms%20and%20accelerate%20investment%20in%20local%20manufacturing%2C%20ultimately%20enhancing%20India's%20resilience%20and%20long-term%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi's%20Masterclass%20In%20Diplomacy%3A%20A%20%26quot%3BMEGA%26quot%3B%20Partnership%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20widely%20acknowledge%20Modi's%20diplomatic%20acumen.%20Top%20American%20analysts%20Ashley%20J%20Tellis%20and%20Lisa%20Curtis%2C%20who%20have%20served%20in%20the%20US%20administration%2C%20lauded%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20%26quot%3Bsucceeding%20magnificently%26quot%3B%20in%20his%20negotiations%20with%20President%20Trump%2C%20despite%20the%20backdrop%20of%20reciprocal%20tariffs.%20Tellis%20noted%20that%20Modi's%20visit%20within%20Trump's%20first%20month%20in%20office%20was%20a%20strategic%20move%20to%20cement%20India%20as%20a%20key%20US%20ally%20-%20and%20he%20achieved%20it%20on%20all%20fronts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20visit%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3BModi%20Makes%20Magic%26quot%3B%2C%20showcased%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20ability%20to%20navigate%20Trump's%20hardline%20stance%20on%20trade%20and%20security.%20%26quot%3BDisarming%20a%20personality%20like%20Trump%20is%20not%20easy%2C%20yet%20Modi%20managed%20to%20do%20just%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Tellis%20observed.%20He%20further%20emphasised%20that%20the%20joint%20statement%20reflected%20Trump's%20recognition%20of%20India%20as%20a%20trusted%20partner%20across%20multiple%20domains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20bond%20was%20further%20exemplified%20in%20Modi's%20signature%20style%20-%20through%20a%20play%20on%20Trump's%20%26quot%3BMAGA%26quot%3B%20(Make%20America%20Great%20Again)%20slogan.%20Modi%20coined%20the%20term%20%26quot%3BMIGA%26quot%3B%20(Make%20India%20Great%20Again)%20and%20emphasised%20that%20when%20the%20US%20and%20India%20collaborate%2C%20MAGA%20%2B%20MIGA%20creates%20a%20'MEGA'%20partnership%20for%20prosperity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Leader%20Who%20Delivers%20On%20The%20Global%20Stage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi's%20recent%20diplomatic%20engagements%20showcase%20a%20leader%20who%20not%20only%20masters%20negotiation%20but%20strategically%20uses%20it%20to%20elevate%20India's%20global%20standing.%20His%20ability%20to%20forge%20critical%20economic%2C%20defence%2C%20and%20technological%20partnerships%20underscores%20a%20vision%20that%20few%20can%20rival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20President%20Trump%20acknowledged%20Modi's%20negotiating%20prowess%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20much%20tougher%20negotiator%20than%20me.%20He%20is%20a%20better%20negotiator%20than%20me.%20There%20is%20not%20even%20a%20contest.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20strong%20diplomatic%20push%20also%20led%20to%20a%20major%20breakthrough%20in%20India's%20fight%20against%20terrorism.%20PM%20Modi%20secured%20a%20commitment%20to%20eliminate%20terrorist%20safe%20havens%20globally%20-%20a%20key%20highlight%20of%20the%20India-US%20joint%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%20of%20Modi's%20assertive%20stance%2C%20Trump%20has%20officially%20approved%20the%20extradition%20of%20Tahawwur%20Rana%2C%20a%20prime%20accused%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks.%20This%20marks%20a%20major%20diplomatic%20victory%20for%20India%20in%20ensuring%20that%20terrorists%20face%20justice.%20Trump%20also%20hinted%20at%20more%20extraditions%20in%20the%20future%2C%20reinforcing%20Modi's%20relentless%20pursuit%20to%20bring%20those%20responsible%20for%20attacks%20on%20India%20to%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20MEGA%20partnership%20between%20India%20and%20the%20US%20unfolds%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20that%20Modi%20is%20not%20just%20shaping%20the%20present%20-%20he%20is%20securing%20India's%20future%20as%20a%20global%20powerhouse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENavigating%20Global%20Oil%20Market%20Prices%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20global%20energy%20markets%20faced%20unprecedented%20challenges%20due%20to%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20and%20subsequent%20Western%20sanctions%20on%20Russian%20oil%2C%20most%20countries%20struggled%20with%20skyrocketing%20fuel%20prices%20and%20supply%20disruptions.%20However%2C%20under%20the%20leadership%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20India%20defied%20the%20odds%20and%20emerged%20as%20a%20strategic%20player%20in%20global%20oil%20diplomacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adopting%20a%20pragmatic%20and%20national-interest-first%20approach%2C%20PM%20Modi's%20government%20skillfully%20secured%20discounted%20Russian%20crude%2C%20diversified%20energy%20sources%2C%20and%20maintained%20strong%20global%20partnerships%20-%20all%20while%20resisting%20Western%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Global%20Leap%20Under%20PM%20Modi%3A%20Strategic%20Benefits%20From%20Russia%20And%20Beyond%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20India%20has%20witnessed%20a%20strategic%20recalibration%20of%20its%20international%20partnerships%2C%20leveraging%20relationships%20with%20nations%20like%20Russia%2C%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20key%20global%20players%20to%20boost%20its%20economic%2C%20defence%2C%20and%20technological%20prowess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrengthened%20Ties%20with%20Russia%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20longstanding%20relationship%20with%20Russia%20has%20deepened%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20energy%20sectors.%20Continued%20arms%20deals%2C%20such%20as%20the%20procurement%20of%20advanced%20missile%20systems%2C%20have%20enhanced%20national%20security.%20Moreover%2C%20collaborations%20in%20nuclear%20energy%20and%20space%20exploration%20have%20opened%20new%20avenues%20for%20technological%20exchange%20and%20innovation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBroadening%20Alliances%20with%20Western%20Powers%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimultaneously%2C%20India%20has%20fortified%20its%20ties%20with%20the%20United%20States%2C%20resulting%20in%20landmark%20defence%20agreements%20and%20technology%20transfers.%20Initiatives%20under%20frameworks%20like%20COMCASA%20and%20BECA%20have%20not%20only%20improved%20military%20capabilities%20but%20also%20spurred%20advancements%20in%20digital%20infrastructure%20and%20innovation%2C%20reflecting%20a%20balanced%20approach%20in%20its%20global%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(The%20author%20is%C2%A0National%20Spokesperson%2C%C2%A0Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A173981