3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnvironmentalists%20also%20attribute%20this%20crisis%20in%20part%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F387852%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-sparkling-mindz-global-school-student-changemakers-urban-planning%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eclimate%20change%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%20The%20Himalayas%E2%80%99%20fragile%20ecosystem%20is%20highly%20susceptible%20to%20shifting%20weather%20patterns.%20A%202022%20study%20revealed%20that%20between%201980%20and%202020%2C%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20maximum%20and%20minimum%20temperatures%20increased%20by%202.00%C2%B0C%20and%201.10%C2%B0C%2C%20respectively%2C%20while%20precipitation%20decreased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20consequences%20are%20significant.%20%E2%80%9CChinars%20are%20crucial%20for%20preventing%20soil%20erosion%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20environmentalist%20Raja%20Muzaffar%20Bhat.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20deep%20roots%20act%20as%20anchors%2C%20and%20they%20are%20vital%20carbon%20sinks.%20During%20the%202014%20floods%2C%20areas%20with%20chinar%20trees%20were%20significantly%20less%20affected%20by%20soil%20erosion.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUsing%20tech%20to%20save%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20chinar%20trees%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Forest%20Department%20decided%20to%20take%20an%20innovative%20step%20towards%20protecting%20these%20iconic%20trees%20%E2%80%94%20a%20unique%20%E2%80%98aadhar%20identity%E2%80%99%20for%20every%20single%20chinar%20in%20the%20Kashmir%20valley.%20As%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20chinar%20trees%20are%20being%20geotagged%20with%20scannable%20QR%20plates%2C%20and%20are%20being%20monitored%20and%20safeguarded%20using%20cutting%20edge%20tech.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20ultrasonography-based%20(USG)%20gadgets%2C%20we%20can%20assess%20the%20health%20and%20risk%20levels%20of%20each%20chinar%2C%20eliminating%20the%20need%20for%20manual%20evaluation%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tariq%20explains.%20This%20technology%20allows%20for%20early%20detection%20of%20vulnerabilities%20and%20targeted%20interventions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20J%26amp%3BK%20Forest%20Department%2C%20spearheading%20the%20campaign%2C%20is%20utilising%20a%20Geographical%20Information%20System%20(GIS)%20to%20create%20a%20comprehensive%20database.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20initiative%20will%20be%20crucial%20in%20protecting%20chinar%20trees%20from%20the%20threats%20of%20urbanisation%20and%20deforestation%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Tariq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201948px)%20100vw%2C%201948px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221948%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Each%20QR%20code%20provide%20information%20on%2025%20parameters%20about%20each%20China%20tree%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575.jpg%201948w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-768x512.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-1536x1024.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3356-1_11zon-1739367575-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-405708%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221299%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEach%20QR%20code%20provides%20information%20on%2025%20parameters%20about%20each%20China%20tree%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScanning%20the%20QR%20code%20provides%20instant%20access%20to%2035%20data%20points%2C%20Tariq%20informs.%20According%20to%20the%20Forest%20Research%20Institute%20(FRI)%20census%2C%2028%2C500%20trees%20have%20been%20tagged%20so%20far%2C%20with%20the%20total%20expected%20to%20reach%2032%2C500%20by%20the%20end%20of%20March%202025.%20Ten%20thousand%20more%20trees%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20geotagged%20in%20the%20near%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20detailed%20record%20will%20enable%20us%20to%20conduct%20ongoing%20research%2C%20identify%20trees%20requiring%20specific%20treatments%2C%20and%20provide%20timely%20care%20to%20prevent%20further%20decline%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Tariq.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20plan%20to%20conduct%20more%20research%20in%20the%20future%20to%20ensure%20the%20health%20of%20these%20trees%20and%20find%20if%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F333910%2Fhyderabad-citizen-group-save-banyan-trees-in-chevella-fight-against-nhai-national-highway%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eany%20tree%20needs%20intervention%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20survey%20on%20the%20geo-tagging%20initiative%E2%80%99s%20success%20is%20still%20ongoing%2C%20between%202021%20and%20today%2C%20Tariq%20says%20that%20there%20have%20been%20no%20illegal%20felling%20of%20chinar%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Athar%20Nagar%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%23%23QA-TP1%23%23%5Cn%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739798442000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FIMG_3539-1_11zon-1739367677.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D405633%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinar%20trees%2C%20which%20once%20stood%20vulnerable%20to%20illegal%20felling%2C%20are%20now%20receiving%20the%20protection%20they%20deserve.%20With%20geo-tagging%20technology%2C%20the%20J%26amp%3BK%20Forest%20Department%20is%20ensuring%20these%20giants%20thrive%20for%20future%20generations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F405633%2Fchinar-trees-of-kashmir-preservation-geo-tagging-aadhar%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pope's%20health%20a%20'complex%20clinical%20situation'%2C%20Vatican%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1739795264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F1a2d%2Flive%2F537ff930-6139-11ee-b101-6f93d6dfbcc2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1kmk09xxdko%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20pontiff%20will%20remain%20in%20hospital%20for%20as%20long%20as%20necessary%2C%20the%20Vatican%20has%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2488%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1kmk09xxdko%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1kmk09xxdko.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fc1kmk09xxdko.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gold%20Rush%3A%20US%20Banks%20Are%20Flying%20Gold%20From%20London%20To%20New%20York.%20Here's%20Why%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20banks%20are%20scrambling%20to%20move%20billions%20of%20dollars%20worth%20of%20gold%20from%20London%20to%20New%20York%2C%20fueled%20by%20fears%20of%20a%20global%20trade%20war%20sparked%20by%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20tariff%20threats%20against%20Europe.%20This%20massive%20influx%20of%20gold%20has%20more%20than%20doubled%20America's%20gold%20inventories%20since%20Election%20Day%2C%20with%20the%20US%20now%20holding%20around%20%24106%20billion%20in%20gold%2C%20up%20from%20%2450%20billion%20on%20November%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gold%20rush%20is%20largely%20driven%20by%20Trump's%20tariff%20threats%2C%20which%20have%20caused%20gold%20prices%20in%20London%20to%20drop%20by%20around%20%2420%20since%20December.%20Traders%20are%20also%20worried%20that%20Trump%20might%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20gold%2C%20prompting%20a%20surge%20in%20demand%20for%20the%20precious%20metal%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20banks%20like%20JPMorgan%20and%20HSBC%20are%20flying%20gold%20across%20the%20Atlantic%20to%20cover%20losses%20on%20short%20positions%2C%20with%20much%20of%20the%20gold%20landing%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20where%20it's%20currently%20worth%20more%20than%20in%20London%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Ffinance%2Fcommodities-futures%2Fwhy-dealers-are-flying-gold-bars-by-plane-from-london-to-new-york-86824199%3Fmod%3Dfinance_lead_pos4%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20This%20development%20has%20led%20to%20a%20significant%20shortage%20of%20gold%20in%20London%2C%20with%20delivery%20times%20increasing%20from%20a%20few%20days%20to%204-8%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C%20Trump%20announced%2025%25%20import%20taxes%20on%20steel%20and%20aluminium%2C%20fueling%20fears%20that%20Trump%20will%20also%20impose%20tariffs%20on%20gold.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Deputy%20Governor%20Sir%20Dave%20Ramsden%2C%20the%20Bank%20of%20England%20(BoE)%20has%20been%20inundated%20with%20requests%20due%20to%20the%20significant%20price%20difference%20between%20London's%20cash%20price%20and%20New%20York's%20futures%20market%20prices%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraph.co.uk%2Fbusiness%2F2025%2F02%2F07%2Fbank-of-england-suffers-exodus-gold-bullion%2F%5C%22%3ETelegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%20Gold%20futures%20in%20New%20York%20