l%20crop%2C%20thinking%20it%20might%20offer%20something%20unique.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201121px)%20100vw%2C%201121px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2F18d4d83c-6342-48ff-90b7-8c9750dba2d6_11zon-1739505765.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221121%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Narendra%2009%20wheat%20variety%2C%20initially%20grown%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20proved%20to%20thrive%20in%20diverse%20conditions%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2F18d4d83c-6342-48ff-90b7-8c9750dba2d6_11zon-1739505765.jpeg%201121w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2F18d4d83c-6342-48ff-90b7-8c9750dba2d6_11zon-1739505765-300x248.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2F18d4d83c-6342-48ff-90b7-8c9750dba2d6_11zon-1739505765-500x413.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2F18d4d83c-6342-48ff-90b7-8c9750dba2d6_11zon-1739505765-768x634.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2F18d4d83c-6342-48ff-90b7-8c9750dba2d6_11zon-1739505765-150x124.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406038%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22925%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Narendra%2009%20wheat%20variety%2C%20initially%20grown%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20proved%20to%20thrive%20in%20diverse%20conditions%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20he%20kept%20saving%20and%20replanting%20these%20seeds.%20He%20managed%20to%20gather%20around%208-9%20kg%20of%20these%20%3Cem%3Edesi%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20non-hybrid%20grains%20and%20sowed%20them%20on%20a%20small%20section%20of%20his%20field.%20Unfortunately%2C%20it%20did%20not%20work%20out%20as%20expected%2C%20but%20Mehra%20didn%E2%80%99t%20give%20up.%20He%20continued%20to%20co