D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895.jpeg%20904w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-800x600.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-600x450.jpeg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-400x300.jpeg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-200x150.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2Ffd142ac5-571a-4806-aeae-4af96831328c_11zon-1739505895-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-406039%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22678%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20getting%20information%20from%20through%20Dr%20SN%20Tiwari%2C%20Narendra%20Singh%20Mehra%20registered%20the%20seed%20with%20PPV%20%26amp%3B%20FRA%20(Protection%20of%20Plant%20Varieties%20and%20Farmers%20Rights%20Act)%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20wheat%20variety%2C%20which%20was%20named%20Narendra%2009%2C%20and%20was%20initially%20grown%20in%20the%20mountains%2C%20proved%20to%20thrive%20in%20diverse%20conditions.%20It%20was%20successfully%20cultivated%20in%20places%20like%20the%20Brahmakumari%20Agriculture%20Unit%20in%20Mount%20Abu%2C%20